<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="4Jun1928"><font color="red">4 June 1928</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Valery Larbaud): &hellip; two U.S.A. publishers to my astonishment have just made me an offer of $11,000 (dico, undicimila dollari) in advance royalties on my &lsquo;work in progress&rsquo;. </div>
